The paper also discusses the use of conflict graphs, which are a type of graph theory, indicating that it could be categorized under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also mentions the use of hypergraphs, which are related to information theory, indicating that it could be categorized under cs.IT (Information Theory).
